Grab your guns.

38:07.686 --> 38:08.820
Fire.

38:08.854 --> 38:09.988
ESME:
When we decided to escape,

38:10.021 --> 38:11.623
we thought we could
save everyone.

38:11.657 --> 38:12.958
We were wrong.

38:12.991 --> 38:15.327
-(collars buzzing)
-(gasping)

38:15.361 --> 38:18.430
(sobbing)

38:18.464 --> 38:20.732
