we couldn't get them out.

38:23.635 --> 38:27.506
We never told anyone
that story before.

38:29.708 --> 38:31.209
Not even Reeva.

38:31.242 --> 38:34.312
I've felt death.

38:34.346 --> 38:37.483
I was a part of my sisters
when they died.

38:39.317 --> 38:43.154
I felt the pain

38:43.188 --> 38:45.290
and the terror

38:45.323 --> 38:46.958
like it was happening to me.

38:46.992 --> 38:48.627
(crying)

38:48.660 --> 38:53.399
And I would do anything...

38:53.432 --> 38:56.668
anything to protect
your daughter from that.

39:00.071 --> 39:02.307
I'm sorry, I just...

39:02.340 --> 39:06.912
I want you to know that, whether
or not you join this fight,

39:06.945 --> 39:11.049
I'm on your side...

39:11.082 --> 39:12.918
