39:35.441 --> 39:38.176
Authorities rolled up
the whole station.

39:38.209 --> 39:40.311
Biggest mutant bust in years.

39:43.281 --> 39:45.451
Not how I wanted that
to go down.

39:50.889 --> 39:52.924
Look, those were
some pretty words

39:52.958 --> 39:54.560
